th the second link assembly)" }}{PARA 215 "" 0 "" {XPPEDIT 18 0 "J[12]
;" "6#&%\"JG6#\"#7" }{TEXT 240 89 " = first flexible link end-effector
 load inertia compounded with the second link assembly" }}{PARA 215 ""
 0 "" {TEXT 240 49 "qd[2] = first link end-effector angular velocity "
 }}{PARA 213 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 239 66 "Tr[12] := kinetic_energy( 't
ranslation', J[12], (qd[1] + qd[2]) );" }}{PARA 216 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 
