ere" }}{PARA 215 "" 0 "" {XPPEDIT 18 0 "T[1];" "6#&%\"TG6#\"\"\"" }
{TEXT 240 35 " = torque generated by the motor #1" }}{PARA 215 "" 0 ""
 {TEXT 240 60 "B11 = first actuated rigid joint viscous damping coeffi
cient" }}{PARA 215 "" 0 "" {TEXT 240 90 "B12 = first link end-effector
